Interface IChannel

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IPrivateChannel, IVoiceChannel
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Channel, PrivateChannel, VoiceChannel

    public interface IChannel
    Defines a text channel in a guild/server.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  IChannel.PermissionOverride
      Represents specific permission overrides for a user/role in the channel.

      • createInvite

        IInvite createInvite(int maxAge,
                     int maxUses,
                     boolean temporary,
                     boolean useXkcdPass)
        Generates an invite for this channel.
        Parameters:
        maxAge - How long the invite should be valid, setting it to 0 makes it last forever.
        maxUses - The maximum uses for the invite, setting it to 0 makes the invite have unlimited uses.
        temporary - Whether users admitted with this invite are temporary.
        useXkcdPass - Whether to generate a human-readable code, maxAge cannot be 0 for this to work.
        Returns:
        The newly generated invite.
